  "2340460": {
    "name": "ONE WAY HOME",
    "steam_appid": 2340460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/a6aac83ede9def1424c110ae14ae2dd2.poster.avif?t=1762597032\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/a6aac83ede9def1424c110ae14ae2dd2.webm?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/a6aac83ede9def1424c110ae14ae2dd2.mp4?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>数千谎言。数百恐怖。十小时。一条回家路</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吉米·泰勒是一个男孩，他发现自己处于家乡神秘事件的核心。傍晚从学校回家时，吉米卷入一场车祸。醒来后，他发现自己身处荒芜街道的一个神秘地方，现在得靠他自己逃脱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >孤独而迷失，他寻找回家的路，一路上遇到未知、有时令人恐惧的谜团与事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">多条道路</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/9892ac308fecd385cc4c75ac8899e7ed.poster.avif?t=1762597032\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/9892ac308fecd385cc4c75ac8899e7ed.webm?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/9892ac308fecd385cc4c75ac8899e7ed.mp4?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吉米将有数条道路可供选择。每条道路都有其独特的障碍、秘密与奖励。通过这些选择，吉米将提升技能、改变故事进展，并接近四种结局之一。帮助吉米打造他独一无二的回家之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">「蜡笔故事」</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/2d392dc31e968db022513609a0564c6d.poster.avif?t=1762597032\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/2d392dc31e968db022513609a0564c6d.webm?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/2d392dc31e968db022513609a0564c6d.mp4?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动画蜡笔画向你讲述这个世界及其居民的故事、秘密与谜团、吉米与他的命运。找到「蜡笔故事」的所有部分，揭开事件背后的真正原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">独特敌人与头目</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/10af5f7e56f75b3f1c10145cb26af7ed.poster.avif?t=1762597032\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/10af5f7e56f75b3f1c10145cb26af7ed.webm?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/10af5f7e56f75b3f1c10145cb26af7ed.mp4?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在路上遇见扭曲的生物，恐怖而令人恐惧。躲藏并逃跑，否则它们将吞噬吉米的心智。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">多样谜题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/5015df1507f75ca1e2b6bde7dc053bed.poster.avif?t=1762597032\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/5015df1507f75ca1e2b6bde7dc053bed.webm?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/5015df1507f75ca1e2b6bde7dc053bed.mp4?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吉米在回家路上将面对许多障碍，只有你能帮助他。展现你的智慧，找到正确的解决方案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">物品投掷</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/ae80a3c19ee11966de349333599be4e1.poster.avif?t=1762597032\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/ae80a3c19ee11966de349333599be4e1.webm?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340460/extras/ae80a3c19ee11966de349333599be4e1.mp4?t=1762597032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投掷不仅能帮助你分散敌人注意力，还能协助解决谜题。吉米在你的帮助下捡起物品并精准投向目标。寻找投掷位置，或许你会发现新事物。</p>",
